      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>. . . [buildings which I declare] for the house-by-house census of the past 23rd year of Antoninus [Caesar] the lord, for which I declare [no one].;(2nd hand) I, . . . ia, also called . . . nis, have submitted the declaration.;(3rd hand) [1st year] of the Emperor [Caesar] Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Augustus [and] of the Emperor [Caesar Lucius] Aurelius [Verus] Augustus, Mesore [. .].</ab>
         </div>
